      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Full length shot of a man wearing a fur cap, a leather coat, light-coloured traditional trousers and peasant shoes (opanki). He is resting his left hand on his belt and is leaning on a stick, which he is holding in his right hand. A painted canvas backdrop is creating the illusion of the scene being set in nature.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Given title by the Austrian Museum of Folk Life and Folk Art: "Bauer aus der Umgebung von Sofia" (Peasant from Sofia vicinity).</ab>
